---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Service" description="ostk Terms of Service — usage rights, license terms, no-account local-first guarantee, website analytics scope, and warranty disclaimers.">
  <main id="main-content" class="pt-16 pb-12 px-4 md:px-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <div class="py-12">
      <div class="section-label mb-4">LEGAL // TERMS</div>
      <h1 class="serif-text text-5xl font-bold tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-6">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="font-body text-xs text-outline mb-12">
        Effective: 2026-03-11 · <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@ostk.ai</a>
      </p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">1. What this covers</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          These terms govern your use of ostk software and the ostk.ai website. The ostk binary is provided under the terms detailed in the <a href="/legal/license/" class="text-primary hover:underline">License</a> page.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">2. The Software</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          ostk is provided as-is. The binary is free for personal and internal commercial use. See <a href="/legal/license/" class="text-primary hover:underline">License</a> for the full grant and restrictions.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">3. No account required</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          ostk runs locally on your machine. There is no account creation, no authentication service, and no cloud dependency. You do not need to agree to these terms to use the software — the License governs that. These terms cover the website and any hosted services.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">4. Website</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          The ostk.ai website provides documentation and benchmark results. We use Plausible Analytics — a privacy-first, cookieless analytics tool — for aggregate page view counts only. See our <a href="/legal/privacy/" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">5. No warranty</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-[10px] text-outline leading-relaxed uppercase">
          THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND, EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. See the License for the full warranty disclaimer.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">6. Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, the maintainers of ostk shall not be liable for any damages arising from the use of the software or this website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="serif-text text-2xl font-medium text-on-surface mb-4">7. Changes</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
          We may update these terms. Changes will be posted to this page with an updated effective date. Continued use of the website after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="font-body text-xs text-secondary">
        Questions: <a href="mailto:contact@ostk.ai" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact@ostk.ai</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
